@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dzpssy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.abs((tmp + 0.27 - v2 + 0.26)))
    v1 = (wp.exp(v0) - v1)
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.cos(tmp + 0.80) / (v0 + 0.26 / v2 + 0.79)))
    data[tid] = v0
